trait-soft-walk-name = Soft Walk
trait-soft-walk-desc = You are careful enough not to step on dangerous spots even without shoes.

trait-freerunning-name = Freerunning
trait-freerunning-desc = You climb onto tables much faster.

trait-sprinter-name = Sprinter
trait-sprinter-desc = You run slightly faster than others of your kind.

trait-fast-lockers-name = Fast Lockers
trait-fast-lockers-desc = You can instantly and as discreetly as possible climb inside a locker or crate.

trait-hard-thrower-name = Hard Thrower
trait-hard-thrower-desc = You throw things harder than others.

trait-poltergeist-name = Poltergeist
trait-poltergeist-desc = After death you become a poltergeist, ooo! However, you can no longer return to life.

trait-voracious-name = Voracious
trait-voracious-desc = Nothing will stand between you and your food! You eat much faster.

trait-drunk-heal-name = Drunken Healing
trait-drunk-heal-desc = You've drunk so much that your body has adapted, turning alcohol into a folk remedy for you.

trait-drunk-tolerance-name = Alcohol Tolerance
trait-drunk-tolerance-desc = Alcohol has less effect on you.
